de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.data

Class DbDataAttributeInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.DbObject
      • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.data.DbDataAttributeInstance

  • public class DbDataAttributeInstance
extends DbObject
    This class is the representation of a DataAttribute instance in the database. It provides the functionality to check for existing instances as well as creating new ones.

        dataObjectId - This is the database ID of the DataObject the AttributeInstance belongs to.
        Returns:
